text.section:
"Cost", as applied to any transportation facility, includes the cost of and all expenses incident to the construction, reconstruction, acquisition, improvement, extension, alteration, modernization, planning, maintenance, and repair of the facility, including the cost and expenses of:
All property acquired in connection with it;
Financial, architectural, consulting, engineering, and legal services;
Plans, specifications, surveys, estimates, feasibility reports, and direct and indirect labor, material, equipment, and administrative expenses; and
Financing the facility, including financing charges and interest before, during, and for 1 year after completion of construction.

"Transportation facility" includes any one or more or combination of:
Airport facilities;
Highway facilities;
Port facilities;
Railroad facilities; and
Transit facilities.
